KH HUr'aNY 'aDNY YHVH VHNH KLVB QYTSh.
VY'aMUr MH-'aThH Ur'aH 'yMVS V'aMUr KLVB QYTSh VY'aMUr YHVH 'aLY B'a HQTSh 'aL- 'yMY YShUr'aL L'a-'aVSYPh 'yVD 'yBVUr LV.
VHYLYLV ShYUrVTh HYKL BYVM HHV'a N'aM 'aDNY YHVH UrB HPhGUr BKL-MQVM HShLYK HS.
ShM'yV-Z'aTh HSh'aPhYM 'aBYVN VLShBYTh 'yNVY-'aUrTSh.
L'aMUr MThY Y'yBUr HChDSh VNShBYUrH ShBUr VHShBTh VNPhThChH-BUr LHQTYN 'aYPhH VLHGDYL ShQL VL'yVTh M'aZNY MUrMH.
LQNVTh BKSPh DLYM V'aBYVN B'yBVUr N'yLYM VMPhL BUr NShBYUr.
NShB'y YHVH BG'aVN Y'yQB 'aM-'aShKCh LNTShCh KL-M'yShYHM.
H'yL Z'aTh L'a-ThUrGZ H'aUrTSh V'aBL KL-YVShB BH V'yLThH K'aUr KLH VNGUrShH VNShQH KY'aVUr MTShUrYM.
VHYH BYVM HHV'a N'aM 'aDNY YHVH VHB'aThY HShMSh BTShHUrYM VHChShKThY L'aUrTSh BYVM 'aVUr.
VHPhKThY ChGYKM L'aBL VKL-ShYUrYKM LQYNH VH'yLYThY 'yL-KL-MThNYM ShQ V'yL-KL-Ur'aSh QUrChH VShMThYH K'aBL YChYD V'aChUrYThH KYVM MUr.
HNH YMYM B'aYM N'aM 'aDNY YHVH VHShLChThY Ur'yB B'aUrTSh L'a-Ur'yB LLChM VL'a- TShM'a LMYM KY 'aM-LShM'y 'aTh DBUrY YHVH.
VN'yV MYM 'yD-YM VMTShPhVN V'yD-MZUrCh YShVTTV LBQSh 'aTh-DBUr-YHVH VL'a YMTSh'aV.
BYVM HHV'a ThTh'yLPhNH HBThVLTh HYPhVTh VHBChVUrYM BTShM'a.
